{"tid":2142793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「火眼實驗室」LIVE","createTime":"2020-08-06T16:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T16:20:08.000Z","uid":231886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce17710a77fbe5e7ec3c235dcd36560998767c4","tid":2142793,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/napowong.hk/videos/1038942039837274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnapowong.hk%2Fvideos%2F1038942039837274&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=09b4eb1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/napowong.hk/videos/1038942039837274</a><br />\n【突發：「火眼實驗室」物資竟出現在中山公園體育館】<br />\n我們剛剛收到街坊通報，中山公園愛有大量警察佈防，而且有幾個大貨櫃車進入中山公園體育館內。<br />\n我們已到現場視察，貨車上印有「火眼實驗室」字眼。<br />\n我們暫時未能肯定政府為何要將物資放在中山公園體育館內，政府事前沒有通知中西區區議會。<br />\n所以，我們懷疑政府已將中山公園體育館用作「火眼實驗室」或甚至早前有報道指紅館或體育館改作「臨時醫院」（香港01消息）<br />\n各位西區街坊注意！<br />\n政府唔封關，連檢疫政策錯漏百出"},{"pid":"3351bb258e67077a3f089e4d9e86d9c8fa6b3510","tid":2142793,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"風水野？<br />\n希望我估錯<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係風水野<br />\n咁多地方唔起 要起係市區 仲要中聯辦附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee840c9396014394df896e18f71abbd4b134dee","tid":2142793,"uid":231886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3351bb258e67077a3f089e4d9e86d9c8fa6b3510","tid":2142793,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"風水野？<br />\n希望我估錯<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係風水野<br />\n咁多地方唔起 要起係市區 仲要中聯辦附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2141510/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2141510/page/1</a><br />\n[整合] 中大湯宿傳銷狗<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">幫手推，要推到傳銷狗仆街</sp